            <div class="BestList-intro">
                <div class="RichTextBody body-2"><p>The technology of cordless vacuums has come a long way in recent years. Once relegated to quick spot cleans only, portable vacuums are now boasting more powerful suction, longer battery life, and more convenient designs than ever, to the point where they can be considered heavy hitters in their own right and earn a spot of honor in your cleaning closet.</p><p>With so many choices on the market, however, it can be difficult to sift through all of the lower-quality models and determine which portable vacuum is the <a class="Link" href="https://www.latimes.com/bestcovery/best-vacuum-overall" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">best choice</a> for your home. Today, we're diving into our top five choices for the best cordless vacuums you can buy in 2023. Whether you're looking for a lightweight option for quick cleanups, or a more heavy duty-machine, we've got you covered.</p></div>
            </div>
        
    </div>

