            <h2 class="BestList-subtitle title-subtitle center">Our Top 5 Picks for Cordless Vacuums</h2>
        

        
            <div class="BestList-container"><div class="ProductReview" id="best-overall-dyson-v15-detect">
    
    <div class="center ProductReview-awardContainer">
        <span class="byline-1 ProductReview-reviewAward">Best Overall</span>
    </div>
    

    
        
            <div class="center ProductReview-image">
                
                    
    <img class="Image" alt="V1_Bestcovery_VacuumGraphics_Dyson V15 Detect.png" width="840" height="560"
        src="https://cdn.bestcovery.ca-times-dam.psdops.com/dims4/default/116f5f0/2147483647/strip/true/crop/840x560+0+0/resize/840x560!/quality/90/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fbestcovery-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F7e%2Fc2%2F6a59226b434da73c1e4dca65a847%2Fv1-bestcovery-vacuumgraphics-dyson-v15-detect.png"
        >


                
            </div>
        
    

    
        <h3 class="center ProductReview-title" tabindex="">
             
                Dyson V15 Detect - Best Overall
             
        </h3>
    

    
      <div class="RichTextBody body-2">
          <ps-toggler data-toggle="review" class="ToggleText " itemprop="description" data-fade-out="true">
    
        <div data-toggle-content
            data-size="large"
            class="ToggleText-content body-1">
            <p>The Dyson V15 Detect is a high-end cordless stick vacuum that excels in cleaning various surfaces and environments, including carpets, hardwood, delicate surfaces like keyboards, crevices, upholstery, and pet hair. Its 230AW suction power and laser dust detection technology are helpful features that make cleaning more efficient and intuitive. The vacuum is lightweight, has multiple brush heads and attachments, and has a large dustbin capacity and HEPA filtration system. While the higher price point may deter some buyers, the Dyson V15 Detect is a great choice overall for customers looking for a high-performance cordless vacuum, earning it a top spot on our list.</p>

<div class="row ProductReview-injectedProsCons">
    
        <ul class="ProductReview-pros">
            
                <li>
                        <span>
                            <svg class="plus-circle-icon">
                                <use xlink:href="#plus-circle"></use>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    <span>Laser dust detection technology</span>
                </li>
            
                <li>
                        <span>
                            <svg class="plus-circle-icon">
                                <use xlink:href="#plus-circle"></use>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    <span>Multiple brush heads and attachments included</span>
                </li>
            
                <li>
                        <span>
                            <svg class="plus-circle-icon">
                                <use xlink:href="#plus-circle"></use>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    <span>Large dustbin capacity</span>
                </li>
            
        </ul>
    
    
    <ul class="ProductReview-cons">
        
            <li>
                    <span>
                        <svg class="minus-circle-icon">
                            <use xlink:href="#minus-circle"></use>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                <span>Higher-end price point compared to other cordless stick vacuums</span>
            </li>
        
            <li>
                    <span>
                        <svg class="minus-circle-icon">
                            <use xlink:href="#minus-circle"></use>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                <span>Some users complain about a high-pitched noise</span>
            </li>
        
    </ul>
    
</div>

<p><i><b>Cleaning Ability: </b></i>Dry, Hardwood, Carpets, Crevices, Upholstery, Out-of-reach areas, Delicate surfaces, and Pet hair<br><i><b>Suction Power: </b></i>230AW<br><i><b>Comfort:</b></i><br>- Lightweight<br>- Fluffy™ brush bar can be washed<br>- Reveals unseen dust to make the cleaning process more intuitive<br><b><i>Battery Life and Runtime:</i></b> 60 minutes<br><i><b>Weight and Size:</b></i> 6.8 lb, 49.6 in tall, 0.76 L (0.2 gal) dust bin capacity<br><i><b>Warranties:</b></i> 2-year warranty<br><i><b>Extras:</b></i><br>- Laser Slim Fluffy™ cleaner head<br>- Laser on brush head reveals otherwise invisible dust<br>- Digital motorbar<br>- Hair screw tool<br>- Crevice tool<br>- Combination tool<br>- Mini soft dusting brush<br>- Stubborn dirt brush<br>- Wand clip<br>- Docking station<br><i><b>Price:</b></i> $$$$</p>
