        <h3 class="center ProductReview-title" tabindex="">
             
                Dyson V8 Absolute - Runner Up
             
        </h3>
    

    
      <div class="RichTextBody body-2">
          <ps-toggler data-toggle="review" class="ToggleText " itemprop="description" data-fade-out="true">
    
        <div data-toggle-content
            data-size="large"
            class="ToggleText-content body-1">
            <p>Like other vacuums in its family, the Dyson V8 Absolute may price out some consumers, though it is relatively inexpensive by Dyson’s standards. Even if comparatively stripped down in features next to the V15 Detect model, the Absolute is still a powerful and versatile cordless vacuum that can handle a variety of cleaning tasks, handling most floor surfaces in addition to crevices, upholstery, delicate surfaces, and still has the ability to clean pet hair. The 40-minute battery life is a little shorter than some selections on this list but should still be satisfactory for small to medium-sized cleaning jobs.</p>

<div class="row ProductReview-injectedProsCons">
    
        <ul class="ProductReview-pros">
            
