        <div data-toggle-content
            data-size="large"
            class="ToggleText-content body-1">
            <p>With impressive suction power and both the longest battery life and highest-capacity dust bin on our list, the Samsung Jet 75 is an attractive choice for those who need to clean larger areas. If you have a large house and want the ability to clean the whole thing in one shot, this is your go-to option. Be aware, however, that its power and longevity come at the cost of nimbleness, as this is one of the heavier choices on our list, weighing in at over 6 pounds. Additionally, the availability of this model and customer support can be limited. Overall, the Samsung Jet 75 is a smart choice of cordless vacuum for heavy cleaning, provided that the weight isn’t a deal breaker for your needs.</p>

